## Design Objectives:
* This design is made to manufacture using a 3-axis CNC carving machine(can be 3D printed)
* There are two plates holding the electronics between.
* For the assembly of the main two plates m4 screws will be used.
* There are 4 pieces which results with a phone holder like structure. That structure holds the assembly of the two plates.
* No ready text type is used in the BBR text applied on the front plate, the text is manuelly modeled.
* HDF wood plates with 4 mm thickness will be used.
* It is suggested to use small(1-1.5 mm) CNC bits for a better result.
